msgid ""
"WP_DEBUG, WP_DEBUG_LOG and WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY are evaluated by WordPress "
"before any plugin loads. For them to have full effect (including showing "
"errors), they must be defined in wp-config.php. This plugin can still set "
"them for code that reads the constant after plugins load, but it cannot "
"activate WordPress's own error display."
msgstr ""
"WP_DEBUG, WP_DEBUG_LOG i WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY es avaluen per WordPress abans que"
" es carregui cap plugin. Perquè tinguin efecte total (incloent mostrar "
"errors), han d'estar definides a wp-config.php. Aquest plugin pot seguir "
"establint-les per al codi que llegeix la constant després de que es "
"carreguin els plugins, però no pot activar la pròpia visualització d'errors "
"de WordPress."

msgid ""
"Writes a config file to wp-content/uploads/tsosk-config/ that is loaded "
"automatically by this plugin. Constants already defined in wp-config.php "
"take precedence and cannot be overridden — they will show an \"Overridden by"
" wp-config.php\" badge."
msgstr ""
"Escriu un fitxer de configuració a wp-content/uploads/tsosk-config/ que es "
"carrega automàticament per aquest plugin. Les constants ja definides a wp-"
"config.php tenen prioritat i no es poden sobreescriure — mostraran un badge "
"«Sobreescrit per wp-config.php»."

msgid ""
"Read-only security review plus safe toggles for WordPress hardening "
"constants. Toggles write a config file to wp-content/uploads/tsosk-config/ "
"that is loaded at plugin init time. Constants already defined in wp-"
